1. cmd to create component:
- cmd: php artisan make:component fileName
- cmd: php artisan make:component FolderName/fieldName

2. cmd to creat component with folder controll
- cmd: php artisan make:component product.form --view
after run this cmd it'll be create three folder as below:
  . resources/views/components/product/form.blade.php
  . app/view/form.php
  .app/Http/Controllers/ProductController.php
